g.text: a) Make sure to align the 8 holes of the arm
on the 2 linear bearing blocks HGH15C
b) Firmly fasten Z printer arm to both HGH15C
c) Position the left rail at a distance of
1mm from the top edge of the C-beam

ShowToolTip(evt,'7',"0257_M4x14 Socket head cap screw black")
